{"id":656685,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/09/【麻辣总局】这条路我们一起加速/","date":"2020-09-29T00:19:40Z","modified":"2020-09-29T00:24:46Z","title":"【麻辣总局】“这条路我们一起加速”","content":"<p>9月26日，新华社发布了一条活动微博，号召为贵州精准扶贫工作带来的变化见证，但因使用了“我们请你一起加速”的宣传语，令广大“<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%8F%8D%E8%B4%BC\">反贼</a>”产生联想，想到近年流行的“<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89\">加速主义</a>”与“<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%80%BB%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%B8%88\">总加速师</a>”，给人一种“敌在中宣部”的高级黑错觉。</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-656768\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速2-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速2-1.jpeg 639w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速2-1-212x300.jpeg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-656767\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速.png 1194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速-300x237.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速-1024x808.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速-768x606.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/一起加速-1080x852.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38827,41492,38912,13789],"tags":[40447,40187,41047,24186]}